headline: Fomento Economico: Q1 Earnings Snapshot
summary: MONTERREY N.L., Mexico (AP) — Fomento Economico Mexicano SAB (FMX) on Monday reported net income of $284.1 million in its first quarter. On a per-share basis, the Monterrey N.l. Mexico-based company said it had profit of 79 cents.
